msgstr ""
"Če uporabnik ne more urediti objavljenega prispevka, zahtevajte zmogljivost "
"edit_others_revisions."

#: admin/options.php:1655
msgid ""
"If the user can't edit the published post, require the list_others_revisions "
"capability."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabnik ne more urediti objavljenega prispevka, zahtevajte zmogljivost "
"list_others_revisions."

#: admin/options.php:1660
msgid ""
"Bypass the above restrictions for others' revisions to logged in user's own "
